<ab facs="#facs_356_r1l18">vnd ʒu Beheim etc kunıgs <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> . <expan>gelegenh<ex>eit</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
